::The Galactors::

The Vycir/Flare jet is engulfed by fire, but it does little to its
armor. Vycir's cloaking system activates, and the jet slowly
dissapears from sight. A few seconds later two grenades fly out of
seemingly nowhere and head toward Sinnertwin.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Supernova/Slasys/Scrap jet spins in the air, avoiding Hun-Grr's
shots and returning fire with two missiles.
